{
 "name": "RPlog_Karaoke",
 "title": "Karaoke at Malif's",
 "summary": "What begins as a small meeting in Malif's Coruscant office to discuss weapons contracts swells into a freewheeling 'Arms ball' of music, liquor, and dancers. The pirate Juran lounges and trades barbs with pilots Liza Molokai, Dante, and Keline, until the old Sith Lord Tyler Damion arrives, draws his blaster to clear the stage band, and declares karaoke night. Tyler and Juran launch into a raucous rendition of 'Alcohol,' and then Dante takes the mic for a string of bawdy fighter-pilot drinking songs to the crowd's delight and Liza's mortification. Amid smashed glasses, spilled ale, and Juran collapsing dramatically off the stage, the party carries on in good-natured chaos as the performers stagger through one filthy verse after another.",
